data.description: New Listing located in Wainsfield Subdivision in Stantonsburg! This spacious floor plan has just over 1600 sq ft with an open floor plan and 1 car garage. Upstairs you'll find 2 guest beds and a large loft area ideal for a home office. You will also love the large primary bedroom with En Suite bath and walk in closet.  Enjoy the beautiful large fenced backyard that backs up to a treeline v/s another homesite! Set up your private showing today!
